{"tid":673875,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵證實高鐵米埔段路軌曾因滲水信號不穩","createTime":"2018-05-22T08:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T09:00:27.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"117ce65dbf0db2afa45fdb34c112696b168009b6","tid":673875,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T08:14:00.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】港鐵證實上星期五高鐵試運期間，米埔附近一段路軌信號系統曾不穩定需要停駛。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵指，事後維修人員到場發現有關路軌，附近地面有水跡，相信是一些地下水，信號系統受潮影響而不穩定。<br />\n<br />\n經詳細檢查，確定路軌和其他設施包括隧道抽水泵運作正常，大約1小時15分後恢復列車試運，事件對行車安全沒有構成影響，亦已通報政府有關部門。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵強調，試運期間無發生類似事件，而所有地下設施都設防水層或疏水系統，防止地下水流入，然而深入地底的隧道要絕對防水，技術上不能百分百做到，地下水仍可能由石層透過隧道壁的接縫滲出，港鐵確認有關路段的隧道結構安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=306666&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D306666%26refer%3D&d=v1TkUrlo%2B04KWALS5dTm4JUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=dab1de86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D306666%26refer%3D&h=da882a9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=306666&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"245630792d5773d1a0b85e17e9acf95f48e7184f","tid":673875,"uid":53554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T08:22:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"81f65ac649f5afdf4122fe3e310f0f71f78b8fb2","tid":673875,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T09:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}